attributes.long-description:
The beloved and critically acclaimed LEGO® Star Wars® franchise is back. LEGO® Star Wars® III: The Clone Wars™, combines the epic stories and iconic characters from the Star Wars® universe and hot animated TV series with all new gameplay features. Build, Battle and Laugh your way through the Star Wars® universe like never before!
